microscopi (0.12.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Refactored mouse handling into dedicated input module.
  * Added full JSON-based measure editor (key M) with validation.
  * Added keyboard shortcut for calibration (key B).
  * Fixed color selection regression after input refactor.
  * Restored precision (decimal) button handling.
  * Fixed origin drawing transformation when rotating.
  * Corrected right panel checkbox offset and indexing.
  * Improved graphical cursor visibility (dual contrast crosshair).
  * Improved text editor visibility under dark desktop themes.
  * Internal cleanup and stability improvements.
  * Fix: correct rotation geometry (base/visual transform)
  * Fix: preview alignment under rotation
  * Fix: gray mode applies only to image
  * UX: keyboard shortcuts (D,C,S,X,R,G,Z)
  * Save device and resolution options in .config file

